<h3>What is <%=t('sufia.product_name') %>?</h3>
<p>
<%=t('sufia.product_name') %> contains curated data, tagged citations, articles
and reports on entomology, epidemiology, demography and interventions to
support malaria eradication.
</p>

<p><%= link_to "Guide", "https://www.vecnet.org/media/tutorials/Digital%20Library.pdf" %> for searching the Digital Library.
</p>

<p>
To improve the availability of publications and datasets VecNet users are
encouraged to upload documents to the Digital Library. The access level is
nominated during the upload process as
<ul>
  <li>Global Access &mdash; Open Access,</li>
  <li>VecNet Users Only &mdash; Available to those with a VecNet login, or</li>
  <li>Private Access &mdash; The depositor assigns access to named users.</li>
</ul>

Read the <%= link_to "guide to upload", root_path+"Guide_to_upload_dl.pdf" %> documents to the Digital Library,
<%= link_to "upload a document", current_user ? new_classify_concern_path : user_login_url(new_classify_concern_url) %>,
or feel free to
    <%= link_to "contact us", "https://vecnet.org/index.php/about-vecnet/contact-vecnet" %>.
</p>

<p>
Try out the new <%= link_to "map-based discovery interface", "https://dl-dev.vecnet.org/" %>.
</p>
